# Solid Guide Set - Formula Guide Coated & Uncoated, Pastels & Neons Guide, Metallic Guide

## Get the Full Gamut of Pantone® Spot Colors for Graphics & Print

Sku#: GP1605B

$ 485.00

Add To Cart

Own the gamut of Pantone Spot Colors in one convenient, cost-saving bundle. The Pantone Solid Guide Set provides the greatest array of Pantone Graphics colors. It includes the Formula Guide (Coated & Uncoated), Pastels & Neons Guide, and Metallics Guide. Get access to 3,255 Pantone Matching System colors – 2,390 traditional spot colors, 655 metallics, 154 pastels, and 56 neons – for branding, packaging, marketing materials, signage, instances where spot color printing is critical, and more. The Solid Guide Set gives designers easy access to both standard and specialty colors printed on four portable fan decks. This convenient, compact reference can go anywhere you go, elevating your collaboration abilities. Ideal for school, studio, stakeholder meetings, press checks, and more, the Solid Guide Set is the ultimate spot color bundle.

